</iframe>');
INSERT INTO quote (quotation, CharID, url) VALUES ('He bails on everybody! He bailed on mom when she was a kid! He-he bailed on tiny planet! And in case I never made this clear to you Summer, he bailed on you. He left you to rot in a world that he ruined because he doesn’t care because nobody’s special to him Summer! Not even himself. So if you really want your grandpa back, grab a shovel. The one that won’t let you down is buried in your backyard! Summer: You’re right!
Morty: Wh-what?! I’m not right! I was using ghoulish overkill! Ghoulish overkill Summer!', 'Morty', '<iframe width="0%" height="0" scrolling="no" frameborder="no"
